title: "Mom, You Look Frightened " Bride Chooses a JUMPSUIT Over a Wedding Dress! | Say Yes To The Dress
author: Say Yes to the Dress
description:
Randell comes into Kleinfield to find herself the perfect wedding outfit and surprises everyone by requesting to try out wedding jumpsuits!
